creator: McClatchy
descriptionHtml:
Connect to the Biloxi Sun Herald newspaper’s app wherever you are.

Receive the latest local and breaking news from Biloxi, Gulfport, Long Beach and the Mississippi Gulf Coast. The Biloxi Sun Herald report on the local topics you care about, including local weather, traffic, crime, sports and national news.

Features of the app include:

• Breaking news alerts and real-time updates.
• The local news and sports topics you care about from around the Mississippi Gulf Coast.
• View stunning photos and galleries of news coverage and events.
• The Biloxi Sun Herald opinions, editorials and columns you love.
• Ability to share stories and galleries on Facebook, Twitter or by email.
• EXTRAS: Your subscription to the Biloxi Sun Herald app comes with complimentary web access to Sun Herald site, as well as access to the eEdition. Subscribe to the app now and get your first month for $1.99. Monthly and annual subscriptions are available for $15.99 per month or $159.99 per year and include unlimited digital access to the Sun Herald app, eEdition and Sun Herald website.


Your subscription will automatically renew each month or year 24-hours before the end of the current period, and your credit card will be charged through your Google Play account at confirmation of purchase unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. You can turn off auto-renew at any time from your Google Play account settings.

Read our Privacy policy here: http://www.sunherald.com/customer-service/privacy-policy/

Read our Terms of Service here: http://www.sunherald.com/customer-service/terms-of-service/
